          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>Question:</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'> After ALL costs, what percentage do we keep?</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
